# McNab Ventures Design System Rules for Cursor

## Project Stack
- **CMS:** WordPress with Timber (Twig templating)
- **Styling:** SCSS compiled to CSS
- **Components:** Custom Gutenberg blocks + ACF
- **Fonts:** Literata (headings) + Fustat (body)

