## Component Architecture

### File Naming
- Template: `component-name.twig`
- Styles: `_component-name.scss`
- PHP fields: `component_name_field` (ACF)

### CSS Methodology (BEM)
```scss
.block { }
.block__element { }
.block--modifier { }
.block.is-state { }
```

### SCSS Import Pattern
```scss
@use '../abstracts/variables' as *;
@use '../abstracts/mixins' as *;

.component {
  color: $color-primary;
  @include breakpoint-up('md') { }
}
```

## Key SCSS Variables
```scss
// Colors
$color-navy, $color-teal, $color-gold, $color-sand, $color-copper
$color-primary, $color-secondary, $color-accent
$color-text-primary, $color-bg-primary

// Typography
$font-heading: 'Literata', serif;
$font-body: 'Fustat', sans-serif;
$font-weight-light: 300;
