```scss
.center {
  @include flex-center;
}
```

### Responsive Typography
```scss
.heading {
  font-size: var(--font-size-2xl);

  @include breakpoint-up('md') {
    font-size: var(--font-size-3xl);
  }
}
```

## Performance Notes
- SCSS compiled to single main.css
- CSS custom properties for dynamic values
- Critical.scss for above-the-fold styles
- Lazy loading for images (loading="lazy")

## Figma Integration
When implementing Figma designs:
1. Map colors to $color-* variables
2. Use typography scale from theme.json
3. Convert spacings to $spacing-* scale
4. Component names should match .twig files
5. Document all interactive states

